aviadcohen24-lock-free-ring-buffer is a header-only library.

To use it in a CMake project:

    find_path(LOCK_FREE_RING_BUFFER_INCLUDE_DIR NAMES "ring_buffer.h"
        PATH_SUFFIXES "aviadcohen24-lock-free-ring-buffer")
    target_include_directories(main PRIVATE "${LOCK_FREE_RING_BUFFER_INCLUDE_DIR}")

Then include in your source:

    #include <ring_buffer.h>
